***  {{ill|Chinoike Jigoku|ja|別府地獄めぐり#血の池地獄|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chinoike Jigoku|qq=}}
***  {{ill|Shiraike Jigoku|ja|別府地獄めぐり#白池地獄|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shiraike Jigoku|qq=}}
